            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Our Goal</h4>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">
                Our goal is to provide open-source intelligence resources for anyone wishing to learn and practice their skills.
                Inspired by the lack of resources online, we took things into our own hands and built a platform from scratch in 
                order to combat this critical problem.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-3xl text-emerald-600">
